title: ‘Euphoria’ Season 2, Episode 7 Recap
description:
Joanna and Nora put on their umbrellas to unpack the latest rainy episode of 'Euphoria.' They discuss high school play hijinks and how creator Sam Levinson may have exhausted the benefit of the doubt.
Hosts: Joanna Robinson and Nora Princiotti
Producer: Steve Ahlman
